Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.26,0:02:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,邁阿密登陸站 沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.26,0:02:58.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,{\pos(893,985)}Miami Landing Station
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:02:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,通信衛星呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,受到了軌道上揚陸城的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,聯合總部、支部的通信全部中斷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.38,0:03:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Alpha隊長呼叫各機
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,現在開始攻擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,飛行部隊被全滅了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,確認到了一架敵機
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Silver-22？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,干擾嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.57,0:03:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,先行的Silver小隊好像已經和敵人接觸了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.70,0:03:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,全機展開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,攻擊一切敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是那傢伙嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,隊長！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.41,0:04:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,愚蠢的原始人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,跪在神的威光之下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:13.14,POS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1418,0)}北京／10:34
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是順服呢 還是毀滅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你們只能二選一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:27.45,POS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1418,0)}馬普托／04:47
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真可悲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:48.26,INEN,,0,0,0,,Wipe out vermin Barbarians!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:53.93,INEN,,0,0,0,,With the supreme key that we hold
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.28,0:04:59.48,INEN,,0,0,0,,Her death delivered the truth to us
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:03.69,INEN,,0,0,0,,All of our love, and Sorrow, Anger
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:10.12,INEN,,0,0,0,,The declaration of war
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:46.05,POS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1418,0)}東京／13:26
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.26,0:04:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,到底怎麼回事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,0:04:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那些就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.79,0:05:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,火星重甲騎兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.52,0:05:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,根本不可能打贏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我們只是螻蟻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.32,0:05:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,跟螻蟻沒有任何區別…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,簡直不費吹灰之力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.73,0:05:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,庫魯迪歐伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,現在應該馬上向新蘆原進軍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我們在公主的命喪之地掛起國旗的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,巴斯就更加出師有名了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我就是這樣打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.03,0:05:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,但首要任務是先鎮壓降落區
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 庫魯迪歐伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,請務必將這件事交給我托利爾蘭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:46.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1220,985)}Trillram
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這是報答長久以來您對我的知遇之恩的絕佳機會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.67,0:05:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,就交給你吧 托利爾蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.78,0:05:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,抓到當地的責任者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:06:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,並搞清公主遇害的詳盡真相
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:03.39,NOTE,,0,0,0,,{\an8}緊急報道
